applications.name: YouLookedAt.me
applications.description: A missed connection is when two people briefly cross paths, feel a possible connection, but don’t get the chance to talk further or exchange contact information.  I once had a brief interaction with a girl. We smiled at each other. I saw her again on a beach, but I wasn’t confident enough to approach her. I didn’t know her name, who her friends were, or where she studied. It was a huge city, and I knew the chances of ever seeing her again were slim unless destiny had something planned. But I wasn’t that lucky. I never saw her again.  Even now, that moment stays with me. I often wonder how two strangers who felt something could they ever find each other again. If they don’t know names, addresses, or any personal details. That question stayed with me and eventually sparked the idea for this project.  YouLookedAt.me is a platform where you can share your missed connection moment. If someone else posts a story that matches yours, you’ll be notified and can start a chat. It’s a space to share real, heartfelt stories, post anonymous notes, and maybe even reconnect with someone you briefly crossed paths with.  It’s all about second chances and real stories because sometimes destiny just needs a little help.

applications.description: 20% of the population is neurodiverse. There is up to a 40% unemployment rate among neurodiverse adults. Elucidare are the world's first AI-powered communication tools designed specifically for neurodiverse professionals.   They help transforms workplace anxiety into workplace confidence through three core features:  (1) Tone Analyzer: analyzes incoming messages and breaks down the emotional tone with precision. No more spending hours overthinking a simple Slack message.  (2) Script Generator: generates three perfectly tailored response options for any workplace situation. Describe your scenario and receive direct response scripts with explanations of why each approach works.  (3) VoicePractice (Premium) converts your scripts to natural speech using advanced AI voices, letting you rehearse important conversations and emails before sending them. Practice your tone, timing and delivery until you feel confident.  The app tracks the users usage, saves successful scripts to a personal library and learns their communication style, creating a personalized toolkit that grows more valuable over time.  Built entirely inside Bolt.new as a solo developer, Elucidare showcases the power of modern AI-assisted development. This full-stack app demonstrates what's possible when neurodiverse minds meet cutting-edge tools.
